He comes to know about this when he  &lt;br&gt;
come out of coma or deep sleep.  &lt;br&gt;
His deep sleep or comma may break  &lt;br&gt;
after 8 hours or after 24 days. &lt;br&gt;
What happened to him during his sleep was because of his Paapam or Punyam?&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
